    narr:generatedFrom "21d3c67b7f019283d704895c05704ec956945568" ;
    narr:narration """This hub defines the core [narrative architecture](narr:Narrative_3) of aswritten, centering on the [bootloading of organizational worldviews](narr:Observation_1) into AI. The trajectory has moved from early [memory-based framing](narr:Position_CoreValuePropInstallExpertise) toward a more robust [agent-deployment ROI](narr:Position_PitchReframeAgentDeployment). The current synthesis posits that [each use case is a steering loop plus a memory substrate](narr:Narrative_SteeringLoopPlusMemorySubstrate), where aswritten acts as the substrate. Recent developments have [demoted 'organizational memory'](narr:Narrative_OrgMemoryDemotedToGovernanceSub) to a sub-use-case of [governance](narr:Narrative_GovernanceAsSpeciesOfSteering), while elevating [Synthesized Individual Intelligence (SII)](narr:Narrative_SII_SynthesizedIndividualIntelligence) as the primary product goal. The founder’s [personal identity](narr:Narrative_QueerRepresentationGrounding) and [vision](narr:Narrative_FounderAsAuthorityLayer) now serve as the authoritative anchor, moving away from engineering-heavy metaphors like [optometry](narr:Position_DropOptometristMetaphor) toward a focus on [opinionated, cited AI](narr:Narrative_OpinionatedPromiseMissingArticulation) that fills the [white space](narr:Narrative_WhiteSpaceMechanism) of model defaults.""" ;
